/*
输入n和m
输入字符串s
循环遍历输入第i个字符添加或删去的花费
区间DP
输入f[1][n] 
*/
#include <bits/stdc++.h>
#define int long long
using namespace std;
const int N = 2005;
int n, m;
char s[N];
int c[255][2];
int f[N][N];
signed main() {
	cin >> m >> n;
	cin >> (s + 1);
	for (int i = 1; i <= m; i++) {
		char op[2];
		int a, b;
		cin >> op >> a >> b;
		c[op[0]][0] = a;
        c[op[0]][1] = b;
	}
	memset (f, 0x3f, sizeof (f));
	for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
		f[i][i] = 0;
	}
	for (int i = 0; i <= n + 1; i++) {
		for (int j = 0; j < i; j++) {
			f[i][j] = 0;
		}
	}
	for (int k = 1; k <= n; k++) {
		for (int i = 1; k + i <= n; i++) {
			int j = k + i;
			f[i][j] = min (f[i + 1][j] + min (c[s[i]][0], c[s[i]][1]), 
			               f[i][j - 1] + min (c[s[j]][0], c[s[j]][1]));
			if (s[i] == s[j]) {
				if (j - i == 1) {
					f[i][j] = 0;
				} else {
					f[i][j] = min (f[i][j], f[i + 1][j - 1]);
				}
			}
		}
	}
	cout << f[1][n];
	return 0;
}
